      AI Automation & <br class="hidden md:inline" />
      <span class="text-accent dark:text-blue-400">Data Engineering</span>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      PUCIT Data Science graduate with 1.5+ years of experience building resilient Python AI pipelines,
       BeautifulSoup scrapers, n8n automations, Next.js apps, and Rails backends.
      <br class="hidden md:inline" /> Based in Lahore — working globally.
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="content">
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2 max-w-lg mx-auto">
