          <div class="text-lg text-muted dark:text-slate-400 space-y-4">
            <p>
              I turn messy, manual workflows into clean, automated systems. My background in 
              <strong>Data Science at PUCIT</strong> gave me a solid foundation in how ML models, 
              embeddings, and classification actually work — not just how to call an API.
            </p>
            <p>
              Day-to-day I build web apps with Next.js and Ruby on Rails, write scraping 
              pipelines in Python (BeautifulSoup, Selenium), wire up n8n automations, 
              and integrate AI layers using LangChain and vector databases.
